{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot28SkeletonModification2DJiggleC","title":"SkeletonModification2DJiggle","symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SkeletonModification2DJiggle","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SkeletonModification2DJiggle"}],"roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A modification that jiggles "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/Bone2D"},{"type":"text","text":" nodes as they move towards a target."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","type":"inheritsFrom","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/SkeletonModification2D"]},{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GodotObject","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SQ","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/SH","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/s12IdentifiableP","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantRepresentable","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/VariantStorable"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/skeletonmodification2djiggle"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SkeletonModification2DJiggle","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This modification moves a series of bones, typically called a bone chain, towa